            <p>8. Is the patient part of the LGBTQIA+ community? (e.g., gay, lesbian, bisexual, etc.). It is fine if not comfortable answering.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
