  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q116_NBB_HEARD
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>For this section, we will be asking about your awareness of NBB, ZBB, and MAIFIP.</p><p>116. Have you heard of the No Balance Billing (NBB)?</p>
