          CEB: |
            <p>The following questions relate to the patient’s most recent experience with ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ as an ~~getvaluelabel(PATIENT_TYPE)~~, where we invited you to participate in our survey on ~~edit("99/99/9999", sysdate("MMDDYYYY"))~~.</p><p>Mga lugar-hulatanan</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>The following questions relate to the patient’s most recent experience with ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ as an ~~getvaluelabel(PATIENT_TYPE)~~, where we invited you to participate in our survey on ~~edit("99/99/9999", sysdate("MMDDYYYY"))~~.</p><p>Mga lugar hin paghulat</p>
