          EN: |
            <p>147. What are the medications that you usually take?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang mga gamot na karaniwan mong iniinom?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Anong mga medisina an pirmi na tigabakal asin tigainom?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsa nga mga tambal ang imong kasagarang ginainom?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano it mga medisina nga imo kasagaran gin-iinom?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
