          CEB: |
            <p>Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Nakakuha ka ba han mga medisina tikang ha GAMOT Package han naglabay nga unom(6) ka bulan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
